## Critical Context
- Original project contained leftover workout tracking code from a different application; this has been removed
- Backend uses JWT authentication with bcrypt password hashing
- MongoDB with Mongoose for data persistence
- Frontend built with React, React Router, and Context API for authentication and theme
- All API endpoints protected by authentication middleware and role-based checks
- File upload validation restricts to safe formats and enforces 10 MB limit
- Approval workflow automatically advances to next role upon approval; rejection requires mandatory reason and sends notifications
- Audit logs capture user ID, action, timestamp, and IP address for critical operations

